{"tid":1365334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［727重要］ 元朗各商戶疑似被「勸籲」星期六暫停營業","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:59:30.000Z","uid":50583,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"412ffa504a378944fde2ed16458e8faac8166f92","tid":1365334,"uid":50583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"今日放工返到屋企食飯，我家人先講起晏晝喺元朗買嘢時，見到啲黑警三個一隊咁逐家逐戶去啲舖頭派紙，隱約聽到話星期六怕有混亂建議佢地唔好開門做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢無影相又拍片，我都唔知佢會唔會吹水或聽錯，所以頭先花左啲時間睇下有無同類消息。<br />\n發現一個專講元朗扮中立嘅專頁都指，食環同一建制議員曾建議元朗兩個街市中午12點前閂門，引起部分商戶不滿，及後改為自行決定。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wR4Gute.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwR4Gute.png&h=032f54b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來再查， 已經有幾間商戶係fb宣布暫停營業，相信派紙勸關門一事係真。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuiW2P6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwuiW2P6.png&h=b9d2bd63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qv12dWN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqv12dWN.png&h=48f09d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（希望大家唔好攻擊呢啲商戶，佢地都係被恐嚇。因建制呢幾日係咁發功話一定會有暴力衝突，就算示威者克制，鄉黑/黑警都未必克制）<br />\n<br />\n令我在意嘅係呢條消息， 有中港巴士宣布727 當日2點後班次停駛。 佢係寫 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「為配合封路措施」</span></span>！ 唔係反對左遊行申請咩？ 點解警方又通知佢封路呀？？？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UeVFK5t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUeVFK5t.png&h=5f0aba9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家當日黎元朗行街食嘢又好，睇名勝買手信或參與宗教活動都好，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">都要準備好一定嘅水同乾糧</span></span>，因為實在唔知有幾多舖被嚇窒。<br />\n<br />\n要是有其他資料歡迎大家補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edcc2da16540282b0620af13d4f0cd7d0557415","tid":1365334,"uid":50583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:14:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9100d5dcb45f85866a054604b9e808b5b761ecb","tid":1365334,"uid":50583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fca5e9038c5f7c4301f742db298925c2fe3733ae","tid":1365334,"uid":77109,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"入元朗行街都唔好喺元朗消費！"},{"pid":"2e84bebb61f0adee8e6dbba741b5bd2666ba7281","tid":1365334,"uid":48667,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:17:40.000Z","msg":"想玩返星期一個招<br />\n等全世界自己嚇自己<br />\n最後無人入元朗姐<br />\n<br />\n中共,牛屎佬啲招數黎黎去去都係個兩招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70339dd83cfe1abc7d5178d26424205bbf4fcc0f","tid":1365334,"uid":50583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:17:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af21e28feeae3be4091cc0170be82b1e929b45c5","tid":1365334,"uid":50583,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"2e84bebb61f0adee8e6dbba741b5bd2666ba7281","tid":1365334,"uid":48667,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:17:40.000Z","msg":"想玩返星期一個招<br />\n等全世界自己嚇自己<br />\n最後無人入元朗姐<br />\n<br />\n中共,牛屎佬啲招數黎黎去去都係個兩招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"覺得佢唔係想無人入元朗， <br />\n我懷疑早就計劃盡情圍攻示威者，<br />\n所以叫啲舖閂門等佢唔使「打錯人」<br />\n大家一定要熟讀地圖，<br />\n最好搵元朗朋友照應集體行動。"},{"pid":"c8de535d42a2642eb28c40f1457f2b425e5cc937","tid":1365334,"uid":50583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2448efb7536c9ed104e2f9b48e1dbbd3a13ed5","tid":1365334,"uid":50583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:28:44.000Z","msg":"呢條未證實， 元朗朋友聽朝不妨問下司機星期六係咪無車搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye